metadata.name: AT NIGHT WITH LOVE
metadata.description:
Sometimes you have to break the rules, every now and then you have to feel free.
Moments of passage that remain imprinted in the mind like tattoos.
Rock, passion, beauty, transgression, sensuality, addictions, Love
this is what this shot is about.
